athletes.Biography: My name is Trevor Ganaway and I'm a junior playing college football for Central Methodist University in Fayette, Missouri while getting my teaching degree. My school is contracted with Under Armour but they got special permission for me to wear Nike Cleats as I wear size 16-18 depending on the shoe. Coming from a single parent home, football gave me not only positive male role models but taught me honor, trust, self discipline and confidence. My team and my coaches are like my second family. Don't let my size fool you as I'm told that I'm pretty fast for a big guy. I'd love to have a business endorse me so that I can represent them with the same passion, honor and dedication that I give my team. Being from Missouri I'm a diehard Kansas City Chiefs fan and hope to enter the draft after graduating spring of 2023.
